<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="red-adj">red <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /red/    美 /red/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>红色的；(因尴尬或生气) 通红的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>turned / went red</strong> with anger. 
他气得脸通红。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[象征左派革命、共产主义] 红的；赤的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Red Army 
红军</p></div></div>